trans-unit.source: The type of elements in the list.
trans-unit.target: 列表中元素的类型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a strongly typed list of objects that can be accessed by index.
trans-unit.target: 表示可通过索引访问的对象的强类型列表。

trans-unit.source: Provides methods to search, sort, and manipulate lists.
trans-unit.target: 提供用于对列表进行搜索、排序和操作的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is the generic equivalent of the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类是泛型等效于<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>类。

trans-unit.source: It implements the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> generic interface by using an array whose size is dynamically increased as required.
trans-unit.target: 它实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>所需使用作为动态增加其大小的数组的泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: You can add items to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> by using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 你可以将项添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class uses both an equality comparer and an ordering comparer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类使用相等比较器和排序比较器。

trans-unit.source: Methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Remove%2A> use an equality comparer for the list elements.
trans-unit.target: 等方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Remove%2A>将相等比较器用于列表元素。

trans-unit.source: The default equality comparer for type `T` is determined as follows.
trans-unit.target: 类型的默认相等比较器`T`确定，如下所示。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements the <xref:System.IEquatable%601> generic interface, then the equality comparer is the <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%28%600%29> method of that interface; otherwise, the default equality comparer is <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`实现<xref:System.IEquatable%601>泛型接口，则相等比较器是<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%28%600%29>方法的该接口; 否则，默认相等比较器是<xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: Methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> use an ordering comparer for the list elements.
trans-unit.target: 等方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>将排序比较器用于列表元素。

trans-unit.source: The default comparer for type `T` is determined as follows.
trans-unit.target: 类型的默认比较器`T`确定，如下所示。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface, then the default comparer is the <xref:System.IComparable%601.CompareTo%28%600%29> method of that interface; otherwise, if type `T` implements the nongeneric <xref:System.IComparable> interface, then the default comparer is the <xref:System.IComparable.CompareTo%28System.Object%29> method of that interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，则默认比较器是<xref:System.IComparable%601.CompareTo%28%600%29>方法的该接口; 否则为如果类型`T`实现非泛型<xref:System.IComparable>接口，则默认值比较器是<xref:System.IComparable.CompareTo%28System.Object%29>该接口的方法。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements neither interface, then there is no default comparer, and a comparer or comparison delegate must be provided explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`实现两个接口，则没有默认比较器，并比较器或比较委托必须显式提供。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is not guaranteed to be sorted.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>不一定进行排序。

trans-unit.source: You must sort the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> before performing operations (such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>) that require the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to be sorted.
trans-unit.target: 您必须对进行排序<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>之前执行操作 (如<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>) 需要<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>进行排序。

trans-unit.source: Elements in this collection can be accessed using an integer index.
trans-unit.target: 可以使用整数索引访问此集合中的元素。

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: 在此集合中的索引是从零开始。

trans-unit.source: For very large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> objects, you can increase the maximum capacity to 2 billion elements on a 64-bit system by setting the `enabled` attribute of the configuration element to `true` in the run-time environment.
trans-unit.target: 对于非常大<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对象，你可以通过设置增加到 20 亿元素在 64 位系统上的最大容量`enabled`到的配置元素的属性`true`在运行时环境中。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 接受`null`引用为有效的值类型，并允许重复的元素。

trans-unit.source: For an immutable version of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class, see <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601>.
trans-unit.target: 不可变的版本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类，请参阅<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601>。

trans-unit.source: Performance Considerations
trans-unit.target: 性能注意事项

trans-unit.source: In deciding whether to use the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> or <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class, both of which have similar functionality, remember that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class performs better in most cases and is type safe.
trans-unit.target: 在决定是否使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>或<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>类，这两种具有类似的功能，请记住，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类在大多数情况下更好地执行，并且是类型安全。

trans-unit.source: If a reference type is used for type `T` of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class, the behavior of the two classes is identical.
trans-unit.target: 如果引用类型用于类型`T`的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类，这两个类的行为是相同。

trans-unit.source: However, if a value type is used for type `T`, you need to consider implementation and boxing issues.
trans-unit.target: 但是，如果使用值类型是类型`T`，你需要考虑实现和装箱问题。

trans-unit.source: If a value type is used for type `T`, the compiler generates an implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class specifically for that value type.
trans-unit.target: 如果使用值类型是类型`T`，编译器将生成的实现<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>专门针对该值类型的类。

trans-unit.source: That means a list element of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object does not have to be boxed before the element can be used, and after about 500 list elements are created the memory saved not boxing list elements is greater than the memory used to generate the class implementation.
trans-unit.target: 这意味着的一个列表元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对象不具有可以使用该元素，并会创建大约 500 个列表元素后保存未装箱列表元素的内存大于用来生成的类实现的内存之前进行装箱。

trans-unit.source: Make certain the value type used for type `T` implements the <xref:System.IEquatable%601> generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 确保用于类型的值类型`T`实现<xref:System.IEquatable%601>泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: If not, methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> must call the <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, which boxes the affected list element.
trans-unit.target: 如果不是，等的方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>必须调用<xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法，框受影响的列表元素。

trans-unit.source: If the value type implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface and you own the source code, also implement the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface to prevent the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> methods from boxing list elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果值类型实现<xref:System.IComparable>接口，并且您拥有源代码，则还应实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，以防止<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>从装箱列表元素的方法。

trans-unit.source: If you do not own the source code, pass an <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> object to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> methods
trans-unit.target: 如果您不拥有的源代码，将传递<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601>对象传递给<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>方法

trans-unit.source: It is to your advantage to use the type-specific implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class instead of using the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class or writing a strongly typed wrapper collection yourself.
trans-unit.target: 它是你使用的特定类型实现的最好<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类而不是使用<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>类或自己编写的强类型包装器集合。

trans-unit.source: The reason is your implementation must do what the .NET Framework does for you already, and the common language runtime can share Microsoft intermediate language code and metadata, which your implementation cannot.
trans-unit.target: 原因是您的实现必须执行.NET Framework 的用途为你已，并公共语言运行时可共享 Microsoft 中间语言代码和元数据，不能实现。

trans-unit.source: F# Considerations
trans-unit.target: F # 注意事项

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is used infrequently in F# code.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> F # 代码中不常使用类。

trans-unit.source: Instead, [Lists](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/83102799-f251-42e1-93ef-64232e8c5b1d), which are immutable, singly-linked lists, are typically preferred.
trans-unit.target: 相反，[列出](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/83102799-f251-42e1-93ef-64232e8c5b1d)，这是不可变、 单向链接列表，通常最好是。

trans-unit.source: An F# List provides an ordered, immutable series of values, and is supported for use in functional-style development.
trans-unit.target: F # 列表提供有序的、 不可变的一系列值，并支持在函数样式开发中使用。

trans-unit.source: When used from F#, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is typically referred to by the [ResizeArray\<'T>](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ee353447.aspx) type abbreviation to avoid naming conflicts with F# Lists
trans-unit.target: 如果从 F # 中，使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类通常由所引用[ResizeArray\<' T >](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ee353447.aspx)类型缩写，以避免与 F # 列出发生命名冲突

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to add, remove, and insert a simple business object in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示如何添加、 删除和插入中的简单的业务对象<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class of type string.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示几个属性和方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串类型的泛型类。

trans-unit.source: (For an example of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of complex types, see the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> method.)
trans-unit.target: (有关的示例<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的复杂类型，请参阅<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>方法。)

trans-unit.source: The default constructor is used to create a list of strings with the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数用于具有默认容量创建的字符串列表。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method is used to add several items.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>显示属性，然后<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法用于将添加多个项。

trans-unit.source: The items are listed, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again, along with the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property, to show that the capacity has been increased as needed.
trans-unit.target: 项被列出，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性显示再次，连同<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性，以显示具有已增加容量，根据需要。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> method is used to test for the presence of an item in the list, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert a new item in the middle of the list, and the contents of the list are displayed again.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>方法用于测试是否存在某个项在列表中，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法可用于插入新项中间列表中，并再次显示列表的内容。

trans-unit.source: The default <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property (the indexer in C#) is used to retrieve an item, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method is used to remove the first instance of the duplicate item added earlier, and the contents are displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 默认值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>使用属性 （C# 中的索引器） 来检索某一项，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法可用于删除更早版本，添加的重复项的第一个实例，并再次显示内容。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method always removes the first instance it encounters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法始终中删除它所遇到的第一个实例。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method is used to reduce the capacity to match the count, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法用于减少容量以匹配计数，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性显示。

trans-unit.source: If the unused capacity had been less than 10 percent of total capacity, the list would not have been resized.
trans-unit.target: 如果未使用的容量过小于 10%的总容量，列表将不具有已调整大小。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method is used to remove all items from the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法用于从列表中，删除所有项和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性显示。

trans-unit.source: Public static (<see langword="Shared" /> in Visual Basic) members of this type are thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 公共静态 (<see langword="Shared" />在 Visual Basic 中) 的此类型的成员都是线程安全。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 但不保证所有实例成员都是线程安全的。

trans-unit.source: It is safe to perform multiple read operations on a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, but issues can occur if the collection is modified while it’s being read.
trans-unit.target: 则可以安全地执行多个读取的操作<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />，但如果在读取时修改集合，可能会出现问题。

trans-unit.source: To ensure thread safety, lock the collection during a read or write operation.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保线程安全，读取期间锁定集合，或写操作。

trans-unit.source: To enable a collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要启用访问集合以进行读取和写入的多个线程，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: For collections with built-in synchronization, see the classes in the <see cref="N:System.Collections.Concurrent" /> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 具有内置同步的集合，请参阅中的类<see cref="N:System.Collections.Concurrent" />命名空间。

trans-unit.source: For an inherently thread–safe alternative, see the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList`1" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 本质上就是线程 – 安全替代方法，请参阅<see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList`1" />类。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that is empty and has the default initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 类的新实例，该实例为空并且具有默认初始容量。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是元素的数目，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 如元素添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，自动增加容量通过重新分配在内部数组所需的方式。

trans-unit.source: If the size of the collection can be estimated, using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29> constructor and specifying the initial capacity eliminates the need to perform a number of resizing operations while adding elements to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 如果可以估计集合的大小，使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29>构造函数和指定的初始容量消除了需要执行大量的大小将元素添加到时调整操作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 可以通过调用减少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或通过设置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性显式。

trans-unit.source: Decreasing the capacity reallocates memory and copies all the elements in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 减少容量重新分配内存并将复制中的所有元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数是 o （1） 操作。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the default constructor of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示的默认构造函数<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型类。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor creates a list with the default capacity, as demonstrated by displaying the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数创建默认的容量，列表通过显示所示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The example adds, inserts, and removes items, showing how the capacity changes as these methods are used.
trans-unit.target: 该示例将添加、 插入、 和中移除项，显示这些方法在容量的变化方式。

trans-unit.source: The collection whose elements are copied to the new list.
trans-unit.target: 一个集合，其元素被复制到新列表中。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified collection and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 类的新实例，该实例包含从指定集合复制的元素并且具有足够的容量来容纳所复制的元素。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied onto the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> in the same order they are read by the enumerator of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将元素复制到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>与它们的集合的枚举器会读取相同的顺序。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements in `collection`.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数是 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是中的元素数`collection`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor and various methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%2A>构造函数以及各种方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对范围进行操作的类。

trans-unit.source: An array of strings is created and passed to the constructor, populating the list with the elements of the array.
trans-unit.target: 创建并传递到构造函数，填充数组的元素列表的字符串数组。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is then displayed, to show that the initial capacity is exactly what is required to hold the input elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性然后会显示，显示的初始容量正是来保存的输入的元素的要求。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="collection" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="collection" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements that the new list can initially store.
trans-unit.target: 新列表最初可以存储的元素数。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that is empty and has the specified initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 类的新实例，该实例为空并且具有指定的初始容量。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是元素的数目，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 如元素添加到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，自动增加容量通过重新分配在内部数组所需的方式。

trans-unit.source: If the size of the collection can be estimated, specifying the initial capacity eliminates the need to perform a number of resizing operations while adding elements to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 如果可以估计集合的大小，指定的初始容量，则无需执行大量的大小将元素添加到时调整操作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 可以通过调用减少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或通过设置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性显式。

trans-unit.source: Decreasing the capacity reallocates memory and copies all the elements in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 减少容量重新分配内存并将复制中的所有元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is `capacity`.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数是 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是`capacity`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29> constructor.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29>构造函数。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings with a capacity of 4 is created, because the ultimate size of the list is known to be exactly 4.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>容量为 4 的字符串的创建后，由于大家都知道列表的最终大小恰好为 4。

trans-unit.source: The list is populated with four strings, and a read-only copy is created by using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 列表中填充了四个字符串，并且通过使用创建只读副本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="capacity" /> is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="capacity" /> 小于 0。

trans-unit.source: The object to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要添加到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 末尾的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Adds an object to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 将对象添加到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的结尾处。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 接受`null`引用为有效的值类型，并允许重复的元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> already equals <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array, and the existing elements are copied to the new array before the new element is added.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>已经等于<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>、 容量的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>增加通过自动重新分配在内部数组和现有元素被复制到新数组中，在添加新的元素之前。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is less than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, this method is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>是小于<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>，此方法为 o （1） 运算。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, this method becomes an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果容量需要增加以容纳新元素，此方法会成为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to add, remove, and insert a simple business object in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示如何添加、 删除和插入中的简单的业务对象<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class, including the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示几个属性和方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型类，包括<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor is used to create a list of strings with a capacity of 0.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数用于创建的字符串列表具有的容量为 0。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method is used to add several items.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性显示，然后<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法用于将添加多个项。

trans-unit.source: The items are listed, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again, along with the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property, to show that the capacity has been increased as needed.
trans-unit.target: 项被列出，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性显示再次，连同<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性，以显示具有已增加容量，根据需要。

trans-unit.source: Other properties and methods are used to search for, insert, and remove elements from the list, and finally to clear the list.
trans-unit.target: 其他属性和方法用于搜索、 插入和删除元素从列表中，最后要清除列表。

trans-unit.source: The collection whose elements should be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 应将其元素添加到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的末尾的集合。

trans-unit.source: The collection itself cannot be <see langword="null" />, but it can contain elements that are <see langword="null" />, if type <c>T</c> is a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 集合自身不能为 <see langword="null" />，但它可以包含为 <see langword="null" /> 的元素（如果类型 <c>T</c> 为引用类型）。

trans-unit.source: Adds the elements of the specified collection to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 将指定集合的元素添加到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的末尾。

trans-unit.source: The order of the elements in the collection is preserved in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的元素的顺序均保留在<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: If the new <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> (the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> plus the size of the collection) will be greater than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array to accommodate the new elements, and the existing elements are copied to the new array before the new elements are added.
trans-unit.target: 如果新<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>(当前<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>plus 集合的大小) 将大于<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>、 容量的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>增加通过自动重新分配以容纳新元素，在内部数组和在添加新的元素之前，现有元素被复制到新数组。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can accommodate the new elements without increasing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements to be added.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以容纳新元素，而无需增加<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>，此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是要添加的元素数。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new elements, this method becomes an O(*n* + *m*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements to be added and *m* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果增加以容纳新元素所需的容量，此方法会成为 O (*n* + *m*) 操作，其中*n*是元素的数目要添加和*m*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> method and various other methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>方法以及各种其他方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对范围进行操作的类。

trans-unit.source: An array of strings is created and passed to the constructor, populating the list with the elements of the array.
trans-unit.target: 创建并传递到构造函数，填充数组的元素列表的字符串数组。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> method is called, with the list as its argument.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>调用方法时，与作为其自变量列表。

trans-unit.source: The result is that the current elements of the list are added to the end of the list, duplicating all the elements.
trans-unit.target: 结果是，列表中的当前元素添加到列表中，复制的所有元素的末尾。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="collection" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="collection" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns a read-only <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> wrapper for the current collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回当前集合的只读 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> 包装器。

trans-unit.source: An object that acts as a read-only wrapper around the current <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个对象，作为围绕当前 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的只读包装器。

trans-unit.source: To prevent any modifications to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object, expose it only through this wrapper.
trans-unit.target: 若要防止对<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对象，仅通过此包装器将其公开。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> object does not expose methods that modify the collection.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>对象未公开修改该集合的方法。

trans-unit.source: However, if changes are made to the underlying <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object, the read-only collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 但是，如果更改到基础<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对象，只读集合反映这些更改。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 o （1） 运算。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings with a capacity of 4 is created, because the ultimate size of the list is known to be exactly 4.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>容量为 4 的字符串的创建后，由于大家都知道列表的最终大小恰好为 4。

trans-unit.source: The list is populated with four strings, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method is used to get a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> generic interface implementation that wraps the original list.
trans-unit.target: 列表中填充了四个字符串和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法用于获取只读<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>包装原始列表的泛型接口实现。

trans-unit.source: An element of the original list is set to "Coelophysis" using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property (the indexer in C#), and the contents of the read-only list are displayed again to demonstrate that it is just a wrapper for the original list.
trans-unit.target: 原始列表的元素设置为"Coelophysis"使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>属性 （索引器在 C# 中），只读的列表的内容将显示和再次以演示它是只是原始列表的包装器。

trans-unit.source: Uses a binary search algorithm to locate a specific element in the sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> or a portion of it.
trans-unit.target: 使用对分检索算法在已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 或它的一部分中查找特定元素。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate.
trans-unit.target: 要定位的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Searches the entire sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> for an element using the default comparer and returns the zero-based index of the element.
trans-unit.target: 使用默认的比较器在整个已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中搜索元素，并返回该元素从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of <paramref name="item" /> in the sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, if <paramref name="item" /> is found; otherwise, a negative number that is the bitwise complement of the index of the next element that is larger than <paramref name="item" /> or, if there is no larger element, the bitwise complement of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到 <paramref name="item" />，则为已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中 <paramref name="item" /> 的从零开始的索引；否则为一个负数，该负数是大于 <paramref name="item" /> 的下一个元素的索引的按位求补。如果没有更大的元素，则为 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" /> 的按位求补。

trans-unit.source: This method uses the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for type `T` to determine the order of list elements.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用默认比较器<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>类型`T`以确定列表元素的顺序。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，并使用该实现中，如果可用。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果没有，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable>接口。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`不实现任何接口，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>引发<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> must already be sorted according to the comparer implementation; otherwise, the result is incorrect.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>必须已排序根据比较器实现中; 否则，结果是不正确。

trans-unit.source: Comparing `null` with any reference type is allowed and does not generate an exception when using the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 比较`null`使用任何引用类型可以允许并且使用时不会生成异常<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: When sorting, `null` is considered to be less than any other object.
trans-unit.target: 在排序时，`null`被视为小于任何其他对象。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> contains more than one element with the same value, the method returns only one of the occurrences, and it might return any one of the occurrences, not necessarily the first one.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>多个元素具有相同的值，该方法返回仅包含一个匹配项，并且可能会返回任何一个匹配项，不一定是第一个。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> does not contain the specified value, the method returns a negative integer.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>不包含指定的值，该方法返回负整数。

trans-unit.source: You can apply the bitwise complement operation (~) to this negative integer to get the index of the first element that is larger than the search value.
trans-unit.target: 你可以应用于此负的整数，以获取大于搜索值的第一个元素的索引的按位求补运算 （~）。

trans-unit.source: When inserting the value into the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, this index should be used as the insertion point to maintain the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 插入到的值时<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，此索引应使用的插入点，若要维护的排序顺序。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(log *n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements in the range.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (日志*n*) 操作，其中*n*是范围中元素数。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>方法重载与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法重载。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串创建并填充了四个字符串，顺序不分先后。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 该列表是显示、 排序，并再次显示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload is then used to search for two strings that are not in the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert them.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法重载然后用于搜索的两个字符串的不在列表中，与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用于将其插入。

trans-unit.source: The return value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method is negative in each case, because the strings are not in the list.
trans-unit.target: 返回值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法中是负数每种情况下，由于字符串不是在列表中。

trans-unit.source: Taking the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of this negative number produces the index of the first element in the list that is larger than the search string, and inserting at this location preserves the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 执行按位求补 (~ 中 C# 和 Visual c + + 中，运算符`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的为-1) 的此负的数字生成大于整个搜索字符串，且插入此位置中的列表中的第一个元素的索引保留排序顺序。

trans-unit.source: The second search string is larger than any element in the list, so the insertion position is at the end of the list.
trans-unit.target: 第二个搜索字符串是大于在列表中，任何元素，因此插入位置位于列表的末尾。

trans-unit.source: The default comparer <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" /> cannot find an implementation of the <see cref="T:System.IComparable`1" /> generic interface or the <see cref="T:System.IComparable" /> interface for type <paramref name="T" />.
trans-unit.target: 此默认比较器 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" /> 无法找到 <see cref="T:System.IComparable`1" /> 泛型接口或类型为 <paramref name="T" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.IComparable" /> 接口的实现。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate.
trans-unit.target: 要定位的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer`1" /> implementation to use when comparing elements.
trans-unit.target: 比较元素时要使用的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer`1" /> 实现。

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: 或

trans-unit.source: <see langword="null" /> to use the default comparer <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果使用默认比较器 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" />，则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Searches the entire sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> for an element using the specified comparer and returns the zero-based index of the element.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的比较器在整个已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中搜索元素，并返回该元素从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of <paramref name="item" /> in the sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, if <paramref name="item" /> is found; otherwise, a negative number that is the bitwise complement of the index of the next element that is larger than <paramref name="item" /> or, if there is no larger element, the bitwise complement of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到 <paramref name="item" />，则为已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中 <paramref name="item" /> 的从零开始的索引；否则为一个负数，该负数是大于 <paramref name="item" /> 的下一个元素的索引的按位求补。如果没有更大的元素，则为 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" /> 的按位求补。

trans-unit.source: The comparer customizes how the elements are compared.
trans-unit.target: 比较器自定义如何比较元素。

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use a <xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer> instance as the comparer to perform case-insensitive string searches.
trans-unit.target: 例如，你可以使用<xref:System.Collections.CaseInsensitiveComparer>实例作为要执行不区分大小写的字符串搜索的比较器。

trans-unit.source: If `comparer` is provided, the elements of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are compared to the specified value using the specified <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> implementation.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparer`提供的元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>与使用指定的指定值进行比较<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601>实现。

trans-unit.source: If `comparer` is `null`, the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparer`是`null`，默认比较器<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，并使用该实现中，如果可用。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果没有，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable>接口。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`不实现任何接口，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>引发<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> must already be sorted according to the comparer implementation; otherwise, the result is incorrect.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>必须已排序根据比较器实现中; 否则，结果是不正确。

trans-unit.source: Comparing `null` with any reference type is allowed and does not generate an exception when using the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 比较`null`使用任何引用类型可以允许并且使用时不会生成异常<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: When sorting, `null` is considered to be less than any other object.
trans-unit.target: 在排序时，`null`被视为小于任何其他对象。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> contains more than one element with the same value, the method returns only one of the occurrences, and it might return any one of the occurrences, not necessarily the first one.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>多个元素具有相同的值，该方法返回仅包含一个匹配项，并且可能会返回任何一个匹配项，不一定是第一个。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> does not contain the specified value, the method returns a negative integer.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>不包含指定的值，该方法返回负整数。

trans-unit.source: You can apply the bitwise complement operation (~) to this negative integer to get the index of the first element that is larger than the search value.
trans-unit.target: 你可以应用于此负的整数，以获取大于搜索值的第一个元素的索引的按位求补运算 （~）。

trans-unit.source: When inserting the value into the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, this index should be used as the insertion point to maintain the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 插入到的值时<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，此索引应使用的插入点，若要维护的排序顺序。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(log *n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements in the range.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (日志*n*) 操作，其中*n*是范围中元素数。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载。

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparer for strings named DinoCompare, which implements the `IComparer<string>` (`IComparer(Of String)` in Visual Basic, `IComparer<String^>` in Visual C++) generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 该示例定义了名为 DinoCompare，实现的字符串将备用比较器`IComparer<string>`(`IComparer(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中， `IComparer<String^>` Visual c + +) 泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: The comparer works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 比较器的工作方式如下： 首先，测试比较是否为`null`，并为空引用被视为小于非空。

trans-unit.source: Second, the string lengths are compared, and the longer string is deemed to be greater.
trans-unit.target: 其次，比较字符串的长度，和较长的字符串被认为更高版本。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果长度相等，则使用普通字符串比较。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串创建并填充了四个字符串，顺序不分先后。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted using the alternate comparer, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 列表，排序使用备用的比较器，并显示再次显示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload is then used to search for several strings that are not in the list, employing the alternate comparer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载然后用于搜索不在列表中，采用的备用的比较器的多个字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert the strings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用于插入字符串。

trans-unit.source: These two methods are located in the function named `SearchAndInsert`, along with code to take the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of the negative number returned by <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> and use it as an index for inserting the new string.
trans-unit.target: 这两种方法都位于名为函数`SearchAndInsert`，以及代码要执行按位求补 (~ 中 C# 和 Visual c + + 中，运算符`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的为-1) 的返回的负数<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>并将其用作的索引插入新的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> can contain before resizing is required.
trans-unit.target: 在需要调整大小之前 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 可包含的元素数目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can store before resizing is required, whereas <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is the number of elements that are actually in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 是的元素数的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以存储需要，调整大小之前而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>是中的实际的元素数目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is always greater than or equal to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 大于或等于始终是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> exceeds <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> while adding elements, the capacity is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array before copying the old elements and adding the new elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>超过<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>时添加元素，通过在复制旧元素和添加新的元素之前自动重新分配在内部数组增加容量。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity is significantly larger than the count and you want to reduce the memory used by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, you can decrease capacity by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly to a lower value.
trans-unit.target: 如果容量将显著大于计数，并且你想要减少所使用的内存<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，你可以通过调用减少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或通过设置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>显式到较低的值的属性。

trans-unit.source: When the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is set explicitly, the internal array is also reallocated to accommodate the specified capacity, and all the elements are copied.

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 必须具有从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中从零开始的索引，在此处开始复制。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements to copy.
trans-unit.target: 要复制的元素数。

trans-unit.source: Copies a range of elements from the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 从目标数组的指定索引处开始，将元素的范围从 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 复制到兼容的一维数组。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to copy the elements.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用<xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>要复制的元素。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 元素被复制到<xref:System.Array>枚举数循环访问的相同顺序<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is `count`.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是`count`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示的所有三个重载<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with 5 strings.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串创建并填充了 5 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: An empty string array of 15 elements is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at the first element of the array.
trans-unit.target: 在创建空的字符串数组的 15 元素，与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29>使用方法重载将列表中的所有元素复制到数组的第一个元素开始的数组。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at array index 6 (leaving index 5 empty).
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于复制的所有元素的数组索引 6 开始的数组到列表 （将索引 5 留为空）。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy 3 elements from the list, beginning with index 2, to the array beginning at array index 12 (leaving index 11 empty).
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>使用方法重载来复制从列表中，索引 2 开始的 3 个元素，使用到数组开始的数组索引 12 （将索引 11 留为空）。

trans-unit.source: The contents of the array are then displayed.
trans-unit.target: 数组的内容将显示。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can store before resizing is required.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 是的元素数的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>需要调整大小之前可以存储。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is the number of elements that are actually in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> 是中的实际的元素数目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is always greater than or equal to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 大于或等于始终是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> exceeds <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> while adding elements, the capacity is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array before copying the old elements and adding the new elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>超过<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>时添加元素，通过在复制旧元素和添加新的元素之前自动重新分配在内部数组增加容量。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索此属性的值的运算复杂度为 O(1)。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to check the capacity and count of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object, and illustrates using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method to remove extra capacity.

trans-unit.target: 创建了列表并将其填充并显示其元素后,<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性显示。

trans-unit.source: These properties are displayed again after the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method has been called, and again after the contents of the list are cleared.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions of the elements to search for.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委托，用于定义要搜索的元素应满足的条件。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> contains elements that match the conditions defined by the specified predicate.
trans-unit.target: 确定 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 是否包含与指定谓词定义的条件匹配的元素。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> contains one or more elements that match the conditions defined by the specified predicate; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 包含一个或多个元素与指定谓词定义的条件匹配，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>是返回方法的委托`true`如果该对象传递给委托中定义的条件匹配。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, and processing is stopped when a match is found.
trans-unit.target: 当前元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>单独传递给<xref:System.Predicate%601>找到匹配项的委托，然后处理已停止。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行的线性搜索;因此，此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> methods on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object that implements <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，其中包含实现一个简单的业务对象<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method and several other methods that use the <xref:System.Predicate%601> generic delegate.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法和使用的其他几个方法<xref:System.Predicate%601>泛型委托。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串的创建，包含 8 不复存在名称，其中 （在位置 1 和 5） 两个以"saurus"结尾。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 该示例还定义一个名为搜索谓词的方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 它接受字符串参数和返回一个布尔值，该值指示是否以"saurus"结尾的输入的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A> methods are used to search the list with the search predicate method, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A> method is used to remove all entries ending with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A>方法用于使用搜索谓词的方法，在列表中搜索，然后<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A>方法用于删除以"saurus"结尾的所有条目。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>调用方法。

trans-unit.source: It traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: 它从开始时，将每个元素传递给反过来遍历此列表`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The search stops and the method returns `true` if the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `true` for any element.
trans-unit.target: 搜索将停止并且该方法返回`true`如果`EndsWithSaurus`方法返回`true`任何元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method returns `false` because all such elements have been removed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法返回`false`因为已经删除了所有此类元素。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 在 C# 和 Visual Basic 中，它不需要创建`Predicate<string>`委托 (`Predicate(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中) 显式。

trans-unit.source: These languages infer the correct delegate from context and create it automatically.
trans-unit.target: 这些语言推断从上下文正确的委托，并自动创建。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions of the element to search for.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委托，用于定义要搜索的元素的条件。

trans-unit.source: Searches for an element that matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate, and returns the first occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 搜索与指定谓词所定义的条件相匹配的元素，并返回整个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的第一个匹配元素。

trans-unit.source: The first element that matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate, if found; otherwise, the default value for type <paramref name="T" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到与指定谓词定义的条件匹配的第一个元素，则为该元素；否则为类型 <paramref name="T" /> 的默认值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>是返回方法的委托`true`如果该对象传递给委托中定义的条件匹配。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, moving forward in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, starting with the first element and ending with the last element.
trans-unit.target: 当前元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>单独传递给<xref:System.Predicate%601>委托，接着<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，从第一个元素开始和结束的最后一个元素。

trans-unit.source: Processing is stopped when a match is found.
trans-unit.target: 找到匹配项，已停止处理。

trans-unit.source: When searching a list containing value types, make sure the default value for the type does not satisfy the search predicate.
trans-unit.target: 在搜索时包含值类型的列表，请确保类型的默认值不满足搜索谓词。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, there is no way to distinguish between a default value indicating that no match was found and a list element that happens to have the default value for the type.
trans-unit.target: 否则，是无法区分默认值，指示未找到任何匹配项和碰巧有类型的默认值的列表元素。

trans-unit.source: If the default value satisfies the search predicate, use the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindIndex%2A> method instead.
trans-unit.target: 默认值满足搜索谓词，如果使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindIndex%2A>方法相反。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行的线性搜索;因此，此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the find methods for the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class.

trans-unit.source: The example for the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class contains `book` objects, of class `Book`, using the data from the [Sample XML File: Books (LINQ to XML)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/94252daf-6097-4625-afc2-0eb778958d4f).
trans-unit.target: 例如<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类包含`book`类的对象`Book`，使用来自数据[示例 XML 文件： 书籍 (LINQ to XML)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/94252daf-6097-4625-afc2-0eb778958d4f)。

trans-unit.source: The `FillList` method in the example uses [LINQ to XML](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f0fe21e9-ee43-4a55-b91a-0800e5782c13) to parse the values from the XML to property values of the `book` objects.
trans-unit.target: `FillList`方法在示例中使用[LINQ to XML](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/f0fe21e9-ee43-4a55-b91a-0800e5782c13)要分析的属性值的值从 XML`book`对象。

trans-unit.source: When searching a list containing value types, make sure the default value for the type does not satisfy the search predicate.

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 返回循环访问 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的枚举数。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Enumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 用于 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Enumerator" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 语言的语句 (`for each` c + + 中`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 隐藏了枚举数的复杂性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建议使用 `foreach`，而不是直接操作枚举数。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器可用于读取集合中的数据，但不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中第一个元素的前面。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性是不确定。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，必须调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数前移到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象，直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最后一次调用到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 无法再次将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 设置为集合的第一个元素；必须改为创建新的枚举器实例。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果对集合进行更改（如添加、修改或删除元素），则枚举数将失效且不可恢复，而且其行为是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数没有对集合的独占访问权；因此，从头到尾对一个集合进行枚举在本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to add, remove, and insert a simple business object in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method, along with various other properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法，以及各种其他属性和方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型类。

trans-unit.source: After the list is created, elements are added.
trans-unit.target: 创建列表后，将被添加元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert an item into the middle of the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用于将项插入到列表的中间。

trans-unit.source: The item inserted is a duplicate, which is later removed using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 项插入是有重复，将在稍后删除使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which the new elements should be inserted.
trans-unit.target: 应在此处插入新元素的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The collection whose elements should be inserted into the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 应将其元素插入到 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的集合。

trans-unit.source: The collection itself cannot be <see langword="null" />, but it can contain elements that are <see langword="null" />, if type <c>T</c> is a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 集合自身不能为 <see langword="null" />，但它可以包含为 <see langword="null" /> 的元素（如果类型 <c>T</c> 为引用类型）。

trans-unit.source: Inserts the elements of a collection into the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 将集合中的元素插入 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的指定索引处。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 接受`null`引用为有效的值类型，并允许重复的元素。

trans-unit.source: If the new <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> (the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> plus the size of the collection) will be greater than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array to accommodate the new elements, and the existing elements are copied to the new array before the new elements are added.
trans-unit.target: 如果新<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>(当前<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>plus 集合的大小) 将大于<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>、 容量的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>增加通过自动重新分配以容纳新元素，在内部数组和在添加新的元素之前，现有元素被复制到新数组。

trans-unit.source: If `index` is equal to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>, the elements are added to the end of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`等同于<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>，元素添加到末尾<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The order of the elements in the collection is preserved in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 集合中的元素的顺序均保留在<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n* * *m*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements to be added and *m* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (*n* * *m*) 操作，其中*n*是要添加的元素的数目和*m*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.InsertRange%2A> method and various other methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.InsertRange%2A>方法以及各种其他方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>对范围进行操作的类。

trans-unit.source: After the list has been created and populated with the names of several peaceful plant-eating dinosaurs, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.InsertRange%2A> method is used to insert an array of three ferocious meat-eating dinosaurs into the list, beginning at index location 3.
trans-unit.target: 创建和使用的名称的多个和平工厂饮食历史舞台，填充列表之后<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.InsertRange%2A>方法用于将三个凶恶肉饮食恐龙数组插入到列表中，索引位置 3 开始。

trans-unit.target: 可以使用下面的语法通过此属性访问集合中的特定元素：`myCollection[index]`。

trans-unit.source: The example in this section demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property (the indexer in C#) and various other properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 本部分中的示例演示了<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>属性 （C# 中的索引器） 和各种其他属性和方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型类。

trans-unit.source: After the list has been created and populated using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method, an element is retrieved and displayed using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 后的列表已被创建并填充使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法，元素将检索，显示使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: (For an example that uses the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property to set the value of a list element, see <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>.)
trans-unit.target: (有关的示例，使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>属性设置的值列表的元素，请参阅<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>。)

trans-unit.source: Visual Basic, C#, and C++ all have syntax for accessing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property without using its name.
trans-unit.target: Visual Basic、 C# 和 c + + 所有具有访问的语法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>而无需使用其名称的属性。

trans-unit.source: Instead, the variable containing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is used as if it were an array.
trans-unit.target: 相反，变量包含<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>就像它是数组使用。

trans-unit.source: The C# language uses the keyword to define the indexers instead of implementing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: C# 语言使用关键字进行定义而不是实现索引器<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: Visual Basic implements <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> as a default property, which provides the same indexing functionality.
trans-unit.target: Visual Basic 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> 实现为默认属性，该属性提供相同的索引功能。

trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小于 0。

trans-unit.target: 或
