trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等于或大于 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the zero-based index of the last occurrence of a value in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> or in a portion of it.
trans-unit.target: 返回 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 或它的一部分中某个值的最后一个匹配项的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中定位的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the last occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 搜索指定对象并返回整个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中最后一个匹配项的从零开始索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the last occurrence of <paramref name="item" /> within the entire the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, if found; otherwise, –1.
trans-unit.target: 如果在整个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中找到 <paramref name="item" /> 的最后一个匹配项，则为该项的从零开始的索引；否则为 -1。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is searched backward starting at the last element and ending at the first element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>向后搜索的最后一个元素开始，在第一个元素结束。

trans-unit.source: This method determines equality using the default equality comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for `T`, the type of values in the list.
trans-unit.target: 此方法可确定使用的默认相等比较器的相等性<xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>为`T`，列表中的值的类型。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行的线性搜索;因此，此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示的所有三个重载<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, with one entry that appears twice, at index location 0 and index location 5.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串的创建后，使用显示两次，在索引位置 0 和索引位置 5 的一个条目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29> method overload searches the entire list from the end, and finds the second occurrence of the string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29>方法重载从结束时，在整个列表中搜索并查找字符串的第二个匹配项。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list backward beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the beginning of the list, so it finds the first occurrence of the string in the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索向后从索引位置 3 开始，然后继续到列表中的开头，因此它在列表中查找字符串的第一个匹配项的列表。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of four entries, beginning at index location 4 and extending backward (that is, it searches the items at locations 4, 3, 2, and 1); this search returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索的索引位置 4 处开始并扩展向后的四个条目范围 （即，搜索位置 4、 3、 2 和 1 处的项）; 此搜索返回 – 1，因为没有的搜索的实例在该范围内的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中定位的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based starting index of the backward search.
trans-unit.target: 向后搜索的从零开始的起始索引。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the last occurrence within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that extends from the first element to the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 搜索指定对象并返回 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中从第一个元素到指定索引这部分元素中最后一个匹配项的从零开始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the last occurrence of <paramref name="item" /> within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that extends from the first element to <paramref name="index" />, if found; otherwise, –1.
trans-unit.target: 如果在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中从第一个元素到 <paramref name="index" /> 的元素范围内找到 <paramref name="item" /> 的最后一个匹配项，则为该项的从零开始的索引；否则为 -1。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is searched backward starting at `index` and ending at the first element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是搜索向后开始`index`和结束的第一个元素。

trans-unit.source: This method determines equality using the default equality comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for `T`, the type of values in the list.
trans-unit.target: 此方法可确定使用的默认相等比较器的相等性<xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>为`T`，列表中的值的类型。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements from the beginning of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to `index`.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行的线性搜索;因此，此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是从开始处的元素数目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>到`index`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示的所有三个重载<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, with one entry that appears twice, at index location 0 and index location 5.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串的创建后，使用显示两次，在索引位置 0 和索引位置 5 的一个条目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29> method overload searches the entire list from the end, and finds the second occurrence of the string.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list backward beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the beginning of the list, so it finds the first occurrence of the string in the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索向后从索引位置 3 开始，然后继续到列表中的开头，因此它在列表中查找字符串的第一个匹配项的列表。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of four entries, beginning at index location 4 and extending backward (that is, it searches the items at locations 4, 3, 2, and 1); this search returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索的索引位置 4 处开始并扩展向后的四个条目范围 （即，搜索位置 4、 3、 2 和 1 处的项）; 此搜索返回 – 1，因为没有的搜索的实例在该范围内的字符串。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is outside the range of valid indexes for the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 超出了 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的有效索引范围。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中定位的对象。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 对于引用类型，该值可以为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based starting index of the backward search.
trans-unit.target: 向后搜索的从零开始的起始索引。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the section to search.
trans-unit.target: 要搜索的部分中的元素数。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the last occurrence within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that contains the specified number of elements and ends at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 搜索指定对象并返回 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中到指定索引为止包含指定元素数的这部分元素中最后一个匹配项的从零开始索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the last occurrence of <paramref name="item" /> within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that contains <paramref name="count" /> number of elements and ends at <paramref name="index" />, if found; otherwise, –1.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is searched backward starting at `index` and ending at `index` minus `count` plus 1, if `count` is greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是搜索向后开始`index`结束`index`减`count`加上 1，如果`count`大于 0。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list backward beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the beginning of the list, so it finds the first occurrence of the string in the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索向后从索引位置 3 开始，然后继续到列表中的开头，因此它在列表中查找字符串的第一个匹配项的列表。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of 4 entries, beginning at index location 4 and extending backward (that is, it searches the items at locations 4, 3, 2, and 1); this search returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法重载用于搜索的 4 个条目，索引位置 4 处开始，并向后扩展范围 （即，搜索位置 4、 3、 2 和 1 处的项）; 此搜索返回 – 1，因为没有的搜索的实例在该范围内的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class are used to add, insert, and search the list.

trans-unit.source: After these operations, the list contains a duplicate.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method is used to remove the first instance of the duplicate item, and the contents are displayed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法可用于删除重复项，第一个实例，并显示内容。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method always removes the first instance it encounters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法始终中删除它所遇到的第一个实例。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements removed from the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> .
trans-unit.target: 从 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中移除的元素数。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>是返回方法的委托`true`如果该对象传递给委托中定义的条件匹配。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串的创建，包含 8 不复存在名称，其中 （在位置 1 和 5） 两个以"saurus"结尾。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 该示例还定义一个名为搜索谓词的方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 它接受字符串参数和返回一个布尔值，该值指示是否以"saurus"结尾的输入的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A> methods are used to search the list with the search predicate method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A>方法用于在列表中搜索与搜索谓词方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A> method is used to remove all entries ending with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A>方法用于删除以"saurus"结尾的所有条目。

trans-unit.source: It traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: 它从开始时，将每个元素传递给反过来遍历此列表`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The element is removed if the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: 如果移除元素`EndsWithSaurus`方法返回`true`。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.

trans-unit.target: 最后，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法验证是否在列表中没有以"saurus"结尾的字符串。

trans-unit.source: When you call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAt%2A> to remove an item, the remaining items in the list are renumbered to replace the removed item.

trans-unit.target: 此外，在列表中的项的数目 (由表示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性) 会减少 1。

trans-unit.target: 使用默认比较器对整个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的元素进行排序。

trans-unit.source: This method uses the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for type `T` to determine the order of list elements.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用默认比较器<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>类型`T`以确定列表元素的顺序。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，并使用该实现中，如果可用。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.

trans-unit.source: This method uses the <xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, which applies the introspective sort as follows:
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用<xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法，它适用反省排序，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: If the partition size is fewer than 16 elements, it uses an insertion sort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 分区大小是否少于 16 个元素，它使用插入排序算法。

trans-unit.source: If the number of partitions exceeds 2 log *n*, where *n* is the range of the input array, it uses a Heapsort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 如果分区数超过两个日志*n*，其中*n*是范围的输入数组，它使用 Heapsort 算法。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it uses a Quicksort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 否则，它使用快速排序算法。

trans-unit.source: This implementation performs an unstable sort; that is, if two elements are equal, their order might not be preserved.
trans-unit.target: 此实现将执行不稳定排序;也就是说，如果两个元素相等，则可能不会保留其顺序。

trans-unit.source: In contrast, a stable sort preserves the order of elements that are equal.
trans-unit.target: 与此相反，一个稳定排序保留相等的元素的顺序。

trans-unit.source: On average, this method is an O(*n* log *n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; in the worst case it is an O(*n*<sup>2</sup>) operation.
trans-unit.target: 一般情况下，此方法为 O (*n*日志*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; 在最坏情况下它复杂度为 O (*n* <sup>2</sup>) 操作。

trans-unit.source: The following example adds some names to a `List<String>` object, displays the list in unsorted order, calls the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> method, and then displays the sorted list.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例将添加到某些名称`List<String>`未排序顺序中的列表对象、 显示调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>方法，然后显示已排序的列表。

trans-unit.source: The following code demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29> method overloads on a simple business object.
trans-unit.target: 下面的代码演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29>简单的业务对象上的方法重载。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>方法重载与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法重载。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串创建并填充了四个字符串，顺序不分先后。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 该列表是显示、 排序，并再次显示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload is then used to search for two strings that are not in the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert them.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法重载然后用于搜索的两个字符串的不在列表中，与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用于将其插入。

trans-unit.source: The return value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> method is negative in each case, because the strings are not in the list.
trans-unit.target: 返回值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>方法中是负数每种情况下，由于字符串不是在列表中。

trans-unit.source: Taking the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of this negative number produces the index of the first element in the list that is larger than the search string, and inserting at this location preserves the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 执行按位求补 (~ 中 C# 和 Visual c + + 中，运算符`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的为-1) 的此负的数字生成大于整个搜索字符串，且插入此位置中的列表中的第一个元素的索引保留排序顺序。

trans-unit.source: The second search string is larger than any element in the list, so the insertion position is at the end of the list.
trans-unit.target: 第二个搜索字符串是大于在列表中，任何元素，因此插入位置位于列表的末尾。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload.

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparer for strings named DinoCompare, which implements the `IComparer<string>` (`IComparer(Of String)` in Visual Basic, `IComparer<String^>` in Visual C++) generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 该示例定义了名为 DinoCompare，实现的字符串将备用比较器`IComparer<string>`(`IComparer(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中， `IComparer<String^>` Visual c + +) 泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: The comparer works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 比较器的工作方式如下： 首先，测试比较是否为`null`，并为空引用被视为小于非空。

trans-unit.source: Second, the string lengths are compared, and the longer string is deemed to be greater.
trans-unit.target: 其次，比较字符串的长度，和较长的字符串被认为更高版本。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果长度相等，则使用普通字符串比较。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串创建并填充了四个字符串，顺序不分先后。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted using the alternate comparer, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 列表，排序使用备用的比较器，并显示再次显示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload is then used to search for several strings that are not in the list, employing the alternate comparer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载然后用于搜索不在列表中，采用的备用的比较器的多个字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert the strings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用于插入字符串。

trans-unit.source: These two methods are located in the function named `SearchAndInsert`, along with code to take the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of the negative number returned by <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> and use it as an index for inserting the new string.
trans-unit.target: 这两种方法都位于名为函数`SearchAndInsert`，以及代码要执行按位求补 (~ 中 C# 和 Visual c + + 中，运算符`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的为-1) 的返回的负数<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>并将其用作的索引插入新的字符串。

trans-unit.target: 例如，将某个项与其自身比较时，<paramref name="comparison" /> 可能不返回 0。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based starting index of the range to sort.
trans-unit.target: 要排序范围的从零开始的起始索引。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer`1" /> implementation to use when comparing elements, or <see langword="null" /> to use the default comparer <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" />.
trans-unit.target: 比较元素时要使用的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer`1" /> 实现，若要使用默认比较器 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer`1.Default" />，则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Sorts the elements in a range of elements in <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> using the specified comparer.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的比较器对 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中某个范围内的元素进行排序。

trans-unit.source: If `comparer` is provided, the elements of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are sorted using the specified <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> implementation.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparer`提供的元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>使用指定排序<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601>实现。

trans-unit.source: If `comparer` is `null`, the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparer`是`null`，默认比较器<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型接口，并使用该实现中，如果可用。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果没有，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>检查是否键入`T`实现<xref:System.IComparable>接口。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果类型`T`不实现任何接口，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>引发<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, which applies the introspective sort as follows:
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用<xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>，这适用于反省排序，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: If the partition size is fewer than 16 elements, it uses an insertion sort algorithm
trans-unit.target: 分区大小是否少于 16 个元素，它使用插入排序算法

trans-unit.source: If the number of partitions exceeds 2 log *n*, where *n* is the range of the input array, it uses a [Heapsort](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heapsort) algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 如果分区数超过两个日志*n*，其中*n*是范围的输入数组，它使用[Heapsort](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heapsort)算法。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it uses a Quicksort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 否则，它使用快速排序算法。

trans-unit.source: This implementation performs an unstable sort; that is, if two elements are equal, their order might not be preserved.
trans-unit.target: 此实现将执行不稳定排序;也就是说，如果两个元素相等，则可能不会保留其顺序。

trans-unit.source: In contrast, a stable sort preserves the order of elements that are equal.
trans-unit.target: 与此相反，一个稳定排序保留相等的元素的顺序。

trans-unit.source: On average, this method is an O(*n* log *n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; in the worst case it is an O(*n*<sup>2</sup>) operation.
trans-unit.target: 一般情况下，此方法为 O (*n*日志*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; 在最坏情况下它复杂度为 O (*n* <sup>2</sup>) 操作。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载与<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载。

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparer for strings named DinoCompare, which implements the `IComparer<string>` (`IComparer(Of String)` in Visual Basic, `IComparer<String^>` in Visual C++) generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 该示例定义了名为 DinoCompare，实现的字符串将备用比较器`IComparer<string>`(`IComparer(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中， `IComparer<String^>` Visual c + +) 泛型接口。

trans-unit.source: The comparer works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 比较器的工作方式如下： 首先，测试比较是否为`null`，并为空引用被视为小于非空。

trans-unit.source: Second, the string lengths are compared, and the longer string is deemed to be greater.
trans-unit.target: 其次，比较字符串的长度，和较长的字符串被认为更高版本。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果长度相等，则使用普通字符串比较。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with the names of five herbivorous dinosaurs and three carnivorous dinosaurs.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字符串是创建并填充一个和示例的名称。

trans-unit.source: Within each of the two groups, the names are not in any particular sort order.
trans-unit.target: 在两个组中，名称不按任何特定的排序顺序。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, the range of herbivores is sorted using the alternate comparer, and the list is displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 显示的列表，该进行排序使用备用的比较器，并再次显示的列表。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload is then used to search only the range of herbivores for "Brachiosaurus".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法重载然后用于搜索"Brachiosaurus"仅草食范围。

trans-unit.source: The string is not found, and the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of the negative number returned by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method is used as an index for inserting the new string.
trans-unit.target: 未找到该字符串，并按位求补 (~ 中 C# 和 Visual c + + 中，运算符`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的为-1) 返回的负数的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28System.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%2C%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法用于插入新的字符串用作索引。

trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> 是否为只读。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only does not allow the addition, removal, or modification of elements after the collection is created.
trans-unit.target: 在创建只读集合后，该集合不允许添加、移除或修改元素。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents modifying the collection; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, the read-only collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 集合是只读的是只是一个集合与防止集合; 进行修改的包装因此，如果对基础集合进行更改，只读集合将反映这些更改。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 检索此属性的值的运算复杂度为 O(1)。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回循环访问集合的枚举数。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用于循环访问集合的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" />。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 语言的语句 (`for each` c + + 中`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 隐藏了枚举数的复杂性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建议使用 `foreach`，而不是直接操作枚举数。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器可用于读取集合中的数据，但不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中第一个元素的前面。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置上，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>属性是不确定。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，必须调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数前移到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象，直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最后一次调用到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 无法再次将 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 设置为集合的第一个元素；必须改为创建新的枚举器实例。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果对集合进行更改（如添加、修改或删除元素），则枚举数将失效且不可恢复，而且其行为是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数没有对集合的独占访问权；因此，从头到尾对一个集合进行枚举在本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。

trans-unit.source: An object that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 可用于同步对 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> 的访问的对象。

trans-unit.source: In the default implementation of <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, this property always returns the current instance.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的默认实现中，此属性始终返回当前实例。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。

trans-unit.source: Enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举整个集合本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> returns an object that can be used to synchronize access to the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A> 返回可以用于对访问进行同步的对象<xref:System.Collections.ICollection>。

trans-unit.source: Synchronization is effective only if all threads lock this object before accessing the collection.
trans-unit.target: 同步是仅当所有线程在访问该集合之前都锁定此对象有效。

trans-unit.target: 下面的代码演示如何使用<xref:System.Collections.ICollection.SyncRoot%2A>C#、 c + + 和 Visual Basic 的属性。

trans-unit.target: 检索此属性的值的运算复杂度为 O(1)。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回循环访问集合的枚举数。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: 可用于循环访问集合的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 语言的语句 (`for each` c + + 中`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 隐藏了枚举数的复杂性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建议使用 `foreach`，而不是直接操作枚举数。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器可用于读取集合中的数据，但不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中第一个元素的前面。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 也会将枚举器放回此位置。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置上，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>属性是不确定。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，必须调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法将枚举数前移到集合，然后再读取的值的第一个元素<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until either <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>属性返回相同的对象之前<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>调用。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 将 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 设置为下一个元素。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>越过的末尾的集合，枚举数定位在集合中的最后一个元素的后面和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 当枚举器位于此位置上，后续调用<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>还返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最后一次调用到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>返回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: To set <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again, you can call <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> followed by <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 若要再次将 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 设置为集合的第一个元素，可以调用 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 并接着调用 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合保持不变，枚举数就保持有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果对集合进行更改（如添加、修改或删除元素），则枚举数将失效且不可恢复，而且其行为是不确定的。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 枚举数没有对集合的独占访问权；因此，从头到尾对一个集合进行枚举在本质上不是一个线程安全的过程。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要确保枚举过程中的线程安全性，可以在整个枚举过程中锁定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要允许多个线程访问集合以进行读写操作，则必须实现自己的同步。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空间中集合的默认实现是不同步的。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个值，该值指示 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> 是否具有固定大小。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> has a fixed size; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 具有固定大小，则为 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: In the default implementation of <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, this property always returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的默认实现中，此属性始终返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: A collection with a fixed size does not allow the addition or removal of elements after the collection is created, but it allows the modification of existing elements.
trans-unit.target: 具有固定大小的集合在创建之后不能再添加或移除元素，但是允许修改现有元素。

trans-unit.source: A collection with a fixed size is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents adding and removing elements; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, including the addition or removal of elements, the fixed-size collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 具有固定大小的集合是只是一个集合的包装器防止添加和移除元素;因此，如果对基础集合，包括添加或移除元素，进行更改的固定大小的集合将反映这些更改。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents modifying the collection; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, the read-only collection reflects those changes.

trans-unit.target: 将容量设置为 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中元素的实际数目（如果该数目小于某个阈值）。

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to minimize a collection's memory overhead if no new elements will be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 此方法可以用于降低集合的内存开销，如果没有新的元素将添加到集合。

trans-unit.source: The cost of reallocating and copying a large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can be considerable, however, so the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method does nothing if the list is at more than 90 percent of capacity.
trans-unit.target: 重新分配和复制较大的成本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>但是，可能很大，因此<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法不执行任何操作如果列表为在多个容量的 90%。

trans-unit.source: This avoids incurring a large reallocation cost for a relatively small gain.
trans-unit.target: 这样可以避免产生的相对较小有所提高大型重新分配费用。

trans-unit.source: The current threshold of 90 percent might change in future releases.
trans-unit.target: 当前阈值的 90%可能会更改在将来的版本。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: To reset a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to its initial state, call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method before calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要重置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>为其初始状态，请在调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法之前调用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Trimming an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> sets the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 截去空<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的容量设置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>到默认的容量。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can also be set using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 此外可以使用设置容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to check the capacity and count of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object, and illustrates using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method to remove extra capacity.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示如何检查的容量和计数<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，其中包含一个简单的业务对象，对象，说明如何使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法以删除额外的容量。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class are used to add, insert, and remove items from a list of strings.
trans-unit.target: 一些属性和方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>类用于添加、 插入和删除的字符串列表中的项。

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method is used to reduce the capacity to match the count, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 则<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法用于减少容量以匹配计数，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>属性显示。

trans-unit.source: If the unused capacity had been less than 10 percent of total capacity, the list would not have been resized.
trans-unit.target: 如果未使用的容量过小于 10%的总容量，列表将不具有已调整大小。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the contents of the list are cleared.
trans-unit.target: 最后，该列表的内容将被清除。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions to check against the elements.
trans-unit.target: 用于定义检查元素时要对照条件的 <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委托。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether every element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate.
trans-unit.target: 确定 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的每个元素是否都与指定谓词定义的条件匹配。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if every element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的每个元素都与指定的谓词所定义的条件相匹配，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If the list has no elements, the return value is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果列表没有元素，则返回值为 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>是返回方法的委托`true`如果该对象传递给委托中定义的条件匹配。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, and processing is stopped when the delegate returns `false` for any element.
trans-unit.target: 当前元素<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>单独传递给<xref:System.Predicate%601>委托，并处理在委托返回时已停止`false`任何元素。

trans-unit.source: The elements are processed in order, and all calls are made on a single thread.
trans-unit.target: 元素的处理顺序情况下，和的所有调用都都是在单个线程上。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法为 O (*n*) 操作，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A> method and several other methods that use <xref:System.Predicate%601> generic delegate.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A>方法和使用的其他几个方法<xref:System.Predicate%601>泛型委托。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字符串的创建，包含 8 不复存在名称，其中 （在位置 1 和 5） 两个以"saurus"结尾。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 该示例还定义一个名为搜索谓词的方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 它接受字符串参数和返回一个布尔值，该值指示是否以"saurus"结尾的输入的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A> method traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A>方法遍历此列表的开头，将每个元素传递给反过来`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The search stops when the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 搜索将停止时`EndsWithSaurus`方法返回`false`。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 在 C# 和 Visual Basic 中，它不需要创建`Predicate<string>`委托 (`Predicate(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中) 显式。

trans-unit.source: These languages infer the correct delegate from context and create it automatically.
trans-unit.target: 这些语言推断从上下文正确的委托，并自动创建。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="match" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="match" /> 为 <see langword="null" />。
